Welcome to Our Wyld Life where host Kristy Titus and her husband, Yogi, take viewers along on their day-to-day lives, full of adventure. After relocating to Wyoming, hunting, outdoor and shooting sports recreation are literally in their backyard. The couple is truly making their home on the range while developing their new homestead and enjoying life in the cowboy state.
In our premiere episode, we show you a little bit of what it's like being a Wyoming resident, in the winter. After a tough start, Kristy makes it a great week with familiar faces and many new ones, in what is one of the most fun shows of the year! If you didn't make it in 2023, it's a must to attend next year! Also, you'll be introduced to the newest (and longest eared) members of the family! Kristy shows off her baby mules...lots more of the mules to come! When they aren't out on an adventure trekking deep into the backcountry with their horses and mules, you'll find them preparing for the next opportunity to do so.
Our Wyld Life presents the journey of life out west in Wyoming.

programme.desc: An architect takes his plans for a unique tiny house to the middle of the Arizona desert. Industrial elements are used throughout the build from toolboxes for kitchen cabinets and an airplane wing as part of the roof framing to Japanese-style room separators and an experimental hatch skylight.

programme.title: Operation Black Biscuit: Infiltrating The Hells Angels
programme.desc: ATF agent Jay Dobyns infiltrates the notorious Hell's Angels motorcycle club in the midst of a deadly biker war over drug profits and territory. Dobyns must first pass a series of tests to determine if he's worthy of wearing Angels' colors and running with the pack. To collect evidence against the gang, the ATF agent must outsmart the club at its own game. But in doing so, Dobyns places a target on his back and puts his family in harm's way.

programme.title: Operation Cayman: Drug Smuggling On The High Seas
programme.desc: South Florida lawman, Jim Sweeting, partners with the DEA to infiltrate a network of drug dealers moving pot and coke via the Cayman Islands. Sweeting leap-frogs from dealer to dealer, busting them one at a time and moving closer to cutting off the Cayman connection. The operation is a minefield of bureaucratic roadblocks and gun wielding traffickers that Sweeting must juggle, while staying inside the lines of the law. If he makes a mistake and his identity is revealed, it will mean certain death.

programme.title: Operation Mr. Untouchable: Dethroning Harlem's Heroin King
programme.desc: Nicky Barnes is Harlem's Heroin King. After serving time in jail for drug dealing, Barnes has learned ways to make himself untouchable and his drug empire is such big business that even the President of the United States has taken notice. It will take patience and street smarts for DEA agent, Louis Diaz, to unravel the viper's nest of Barnes' associates and bring them all to justice - and for Diaz himself to stay alive.

programme.desc: ATF agent Jay Dobyns infiltrates the notorious Hell's Angels motorcycle club in the midst of a deadly biker war over drug profits and territory. Dobyns must first pass a series of tests to determine if he's worthy of wearing Angels' colors and running with the pack. programme.title: Operation Cayman: Drug Smuggling On The High Seas
programme.desc: South Florida lawman, Jim Sweeting, partners with the DEA to infiltrate a network of drug dealers moving pot and coke via the Cayman Islands. Sweeting leap-frogs from dealer to dealer, busting them one at a time and moving closer to cutting off the Cayman connection. The operation is a minefield of bureaucratic roadblocks and gun wielding traffickers that Sweeting must juggle, while staying inside the lines of the law. If he makes a mistake and his identity is revealed, it will mean certain death.

programme.title: Operation Mr. Untouchable: Dethroning Harlem's Heroin King

programme.title: Operation Cayman: Drug Smuggling On The High Seas
programme.desc: South Florida lawman, Jim Sweeting, partners with the DEA to infiltrate a network of drug dealers moving pot and coke via the Cayman Islands. Sweeting leap-frogs from dealer to dealer, busting them one at a time and moving closer to cutting off the Cayman connection. The operation is a minefield of bureaucratic roadblocks and gun wielding traffickers that Sweeting must juggle, while staying inside the lines of the law. If he makes a mistake and his identity is revealed, it will mean certain death.

programme.desc: Nicky Barnes is Harlem's Heroin King. After serving time in jail for drug dealing, Barnes has learned ways to make himself untouchable and his drug empire is such big business that even the President of the United States has taken notice. It will take patience and street smarts for DEA agent, Louis Diaz, to unravel the viper's nest of Barnes' associates and bring them all to justice - and for Diaz himself to stay alive.

programme.title: Operation Black Biscuit: Infiltrating The Hells Angels
programme.desc: ATF agent Jay Dobyns infiltrates the notorious Hell's Angels motorcycle club in the midst of a deadly biker war over drug profits and territory. Dobyns must first pass a series of tests to determine if he's worthy of wearing Angels' colors and running with the pack. To collect evidence against the gang, the ATF agent must outsmart the club at its own game. But in doing so, Dobyns places a target on his back and puts his family in harm's way.

programme.title: Operation Cayman: Drug Smuggling On The High Seas
programme.desc: South Florida lawman, Jim Sweeting, partners with the DEA to infiltrate a network of drug dealers moving pot and coke via the Cayman Islands. Sweeting leap-frogs from dealer to dealer, busting them one at a time and moving closer to cutting off the Cayman connection. The operation is a minefield of bureaucratic roadblocks and gun wielding traffickers that Sweeting must juggle, while staying inside the lines of the law. If he makes a mistake and his identity is revealed, it will mean certain death.
